@startuml
!theme plain
title Chart D: Layer Latency Topology

robust "User Perception" as L1
robust "Gateway Processing" as L2
robust "Orchestration" as L3
robust "Deep Reasoning" as L4
robust "Data Fetch" as L5

@0
L1 is Active

@+100
L1 is Idle
L2 is Active

@+50
L2 is Idle
L3 is Active

@+200
L3 is Idle
L4 is Active

@+1000
L4 is Waiting
L5 is Active

@+500
L5 is Idle
L4 is Active

@+5000
L4 is Idle
L1 is Active

@enduml
